---
title: Cal Smart Honey Pork Chops with Broccoli and Garlicky Rice
description: Sweet and savoury meet in our honey-glazed pork chops with stir-fried broccoli. Bold garlic, zesty green onions and sweet honey lighten up this swap on takeout.

